        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–17. Several known taxa in Pinnularia section Distantes found in Byers Peninsula. Fig. 1. LM view of Pinnularia obaesa. Fig. 2. SEM, detail of external view of the special alveolus structure of P. obaesa. Figs 3–4. LM of P. australorabenhorstii. Figs 5–6. LM of P. rabenhorstii. Figs. 7–10. LM of P. borealis var. borealis. Figs 11–14. LM of P. borealis var. scalaris. Figs. 15–17. LM of P. rabenhorstii var. subantarctica. Scale bar = 10 µm, except fig. 2, scale bar = 1 µm." ;
